{
  "stem": "5758.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can do now-- the-- the-- the leaders of the camp said, look here, I think we all should try to run away and go.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some could go to France.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some-- maybe if you go to the coast, maybe you can get a ship, go to England, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went with a group of boys to-- walked from-- from [NON-ENGLISH] to-- towards France.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were able to-- we arrived at a bigger town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wish I remembered the name of the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were at the station, trying to take a train at the station, when the German planes came, and they bombed this particular station.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were really in the middle of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- I was just-- they were building a-- some building material, and I was hiding underneath some big tubes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and the bombs were really falling all around, and we lost quite a few people in that-- in that raid, quite a few boys.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We went-- we walked from there to-- towards the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We crossed the border and arrived in Lille.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In Lille, we were arrested by the French police, asked for identification papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I showed them my passport, my German passport, which had on it a big red J on it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I told him, look, we are Jews, refugees from Nazis, and we're coming to run away from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, no, you are German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You are enemy alien.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they arrested us and taking us to-- by train for-- it took us nearly two days to arrive to a camp, which was called Saint-Cyprien.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Saint-Cyprien was right on the Spanish border, near the Spanish border.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
